输入 Shikari、最后的晚宴、建筑师和更多人签署“停火音乐”公开信https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-the-last-dinner-party-architects-and-more-sign-open-letter-for-music-for-a-ceasefire-3536081？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=进入shikari-最后的晚餐派对建筑师和更多签署停火音乐的公开信Elizabeth AubreyFri, 10 Nov 2023 14:14:03 +0000 Music NewsNews..IndiePopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3536081 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="输入Shikari，最后的晚宴，建筑师" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这封信呼吁“立即在加沙停火”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-the-last-dinner-party-architects-and-more-sign-open-letter-for-music-for-a-ceasefire-3536081">《Enter Shikari》、《最后的晚宴》、建筑师和更多人为“停火音乐”签名的公开信</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="输入Shikari，最后的晚宴，建筑师" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Enter-Shikari-Last-Dinner-Party-Architects-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enter-shikari">Shikari</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/architects">Architects</a>等一群音乐家签署了一封公开信，呼吁在以色列和加沙的战争仍在继续时停火。</p><p>由前工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾创立的<a href="http://bit.ly/MusicForACeasefire" target="_blank" rel="noopener">和平与正义项目</a>今天（11 月 10 日）发布了来自艺术家、音乐家和表演者的#MusicForACeasefire 公开信，“呼吁结束对加沙的围困”。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/liveblog/2023/11/9/israel-gaza-war-live-day-34" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>半岛电视台</em></a>报道，自10月7日以来，加沙地带至少有10812名巴勒斯坦人在以色列袭击中丧生。同期在以色列，死亡人数超过1400人。</p><p>这封信还得到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">《英语老师》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-blessed-madonna">《圣母玛利亚》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/king-gizzard-and-the-lizard-wizard">《吉扎德国王和蜥蜴巫师》等</a>艺术家的签名，呼吁“立即在加沙停火，并结束对巴勒斯坦的轰炸，这场轰炸已经夺走了一万多人的生命”。无辜平民、援助人员和记者。”</p><p>信中还写道：“联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯表示，加沙正在成为‘儿童的墓地’，在破坏仍在继续的同时，英国和美国政府未能捍卫人类，谴责对巴勒斯坦人民的集体惩罚并倡导和平而不是流血。</p><p> “停火将使加沙的人道主义援助不受阻碍，世界卫生组织表示，这场冲突中 220 万平民的死亡和痛苦程度‘难以估量’。”</p><p>它的结论是：“我们是一个由艺术家、音乐家和表演者组成的多元化联盟，呼吁结束对加沙的围困，立即为许多被困在废墟中的受惊、饥饿和受伤的平民提供人道主义援助，并要求我们的政治领导人进行有意义的外交干预促进释放人质、结束以色列对巴勒斯坦的非法占领并实现该地区的持久和平。”</p><p>完整的签署者名单可以在这里查看：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们发起了艺术家、音乐家和表演者的<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/MusicForACeasefire?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#MusicForACeasefire</a>公开信，呼吁结束对加沙的围困。</p><p>阅读公开信： <a href="https://t.co/A2ir99v7tz">https://t.co/A2ir99v7tz</a> <a href="https://t.co/Bdcb8z8hWM">pic.twitter.com/Bdcb8z8hWM</a></p><p> - 和平与正义项目 (@corbyn_project) <a href="https://twitter.com/corbyn_project/status/1722958590737027220?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 10 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>最近几周，许多音乐界的艺术家都公开谈论了这场冲突。本月早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/macklemore">麦克勒莫尔</a>在亲巴勒斯坦集会上发表讲话，称这场冲突是“种族灭绝”，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/killer-mike">杀手迈克</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">迈克尔·斯蒂普</a>等人则<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-michael-stipe-killer-mike-more-sign-open-letter-joe-biden-gaza-ceasefire-3522135">给拜登总统写了一封公开信，</a>要求“立即缓和冲突并停火”。加沙和以色列，以免又一个生命丧生。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gal-gadot">盖尔·加朵</a>(Gal Gadot)、克里斯·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-pine">派恩 (Chris Pine)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-hamill">马克·哈米尔 (Mark Hamill</a> ) 和杰米·李·柯蒂斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-lee-curtis">Jamie Lee Curtis)</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hollywood-stars-sign-open-letter-support-israel-3514639">等 700 名好莱坞明星签署了一封公开信，表达对以色列的支持，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/selena-gomez">赛琳娜·戈麦斯 (Selena Gomez</a> ) 的化妆品公司 Rare Beauty 则宣布将向以色列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-makeup-brand-to-donate-funds-to-the-gaza-relief-efforts-3534155">的救援工作捐款。加沙。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tilda-swinton-steve-coogan-and-massive-attacks-robert-del-naja-among-2000-artists-calling-for-gaza-ceasefire-in-open-letter-3516616">来自艺术界的 2000 多名人士</a>，包括蒂尔达·斯文顿 (Tilda Swinton)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a>的罗伯特·德尔·纳贾 (Robert Del Naja) 和米里亚姆·马戈伊尔斯 (Miriam Margoyles) 签署了一封公开信，呼吁停火。</p><p>同样，麦当娜<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-on-israel-hamas-conflict-how-can-human-beings-be-so-cruel-to-one-another-3518887">在 O2 舞台上谈到了这一情况</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">汤姆·莫雷洛</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-morello-calls-for-condemnation-of-harm-to-all-children-no-matter-who-they-are-after-jamie-lee-curtis-deletes-photo-of-palestinians-3513188">则呼吁谴责对所有儿童的伤害，</a> “无论他们是谁”。</p><p>最近，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-vylan">鲍勃·维兰 (Bob Vylan)</a>指责<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleaford-mods">Sleaford Mods</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">IDLES</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-vylan-call-out-cowardly-sleaford-mods-and-idles-for-not-speaking-out-on-palestine-3536053">没有公开支持巴勒斯坦。</a></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-the-last-dinner-party-architects-and-more-sign-open-letter-for-music-for-a-ceasefire-3536081">《Enter Shikari》、《最后的晚宴》、建筑师和更多人为“停火音乐”签名的公开信</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
