铁娘子乐队成员布鲁斯·迪金森将主演 ABBA 风格的恐怖电影《死者比约恩》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-bruce-dickinson-to-star-in-abba-horror-movie-bjorn-of-the-dead-3536021?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=铁娘子布鲁斯·迪金森主演阿巴恐怖电影《死者比约恩》Liberty Dunworth Fri, 10 Nov 2023 11:43:00 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsMetalPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3536021 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="ABBA 和铁娘子乐队的布鲁斯·迪金森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这部电影是由他的儿子奥斯汀编剧的</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-bruce-dickinson-to-star-in-abba-horror-movie-bjorn-of-the-dead-3536021">《铁娘子》中的布鲁斯·迪金森 (Bruce Dickinson) 将出演 ABBA 风格的恐怖电影《死者比约恩》(Bjorn Of The Dead)，该消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="ABBA 和铁娘子乐队的布鲁斯·迪金森" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ABBA-Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iron-maiden">《铁娘子》</a>中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-dickinson">布鲁斯·迪金森</a>将主演一部受<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a>启发的恐怖电影，名为<em>《死者比约恩》</em> 。</p><p>这一消息是在这位标志性金属主唱宣布他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-bruce-dickinson-announces-solo-single-afterglow-of-ragnarok-uk-ireland-tour-tickets-3532054">即将举行的个人巡演</a>的细节后不久发布的，并将让他在一部末日僵尸主题电影中担任主角。</p><p> According to a report by <a href="https://deadline.com/2023/11/bruce-dickinson-horror-movie-bjorn-of-the-dead-1235595790/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a> , Dickinson signed on to star in the project – which will centre on an ABBA tribute band who get trapped in a nightclub with other tribute acts just as an apocalypse starts.</p><p> “Bjorn and his band must work together to save themselves, humanity, and the future of music,” it reads.</p><p> The Iron Maiden frontman is one of several famous faces from the rock and metal scene to appear in <em>Bjorn Of The Dead</em> , according to the outlet, although no other names have been announced at the time of writing.</p><p> The upcoming horror was written by the singer&#39;s son, Austin, who is also a rock vocalist for London bands As Lions and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rise-to-remain">Rise To Remain</a> . The premise is also based on the original story by Andrew Prendergast, who is producing the movie alongside Austin. </p><figure id="attachment_3536025" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3536025" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3536025" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson-2023@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Bruce Dickinson of Iron Maiden performs onstage during the Power Trip music festival at Empire Polo Club on October 06, 2023" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3536025" class="wp-caption-text"> Bruce Dickinson of Iron Maiden performs onstage during the Power Trip music festival at Empire Polo Club on October 06, 2023. CREDIT: Kevin Mazur/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Directed by Elza Kephart, filming is set to start next year and speaking with the outlet, Austin said he was “honoured” to be working on “this crazy adventure”.</p><p> “Andrew, Elza, and myself can&#39;t wait for you guys to see what&#39;s in store,” he said. “Get your spandex on, preen your wigs, and sharpen your axes. Bjorn is coming.”</p><p> Prendergast added a similar sentiment, stating: “We are thrilled to be making this blood-drenched gore fest from Austin&#39;s super funny, terrifying, cautionary tale about the inner workings of the music industry.”</p><p> Details of Bruce Dickinson&#39;s involvement in the forthcoming film arrive shortly after he revealed plans for a new solo album.</p><p> First announced back in September, the upcoming LP is titled <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maidens-bruce-dickinson-announces-new-solo-album-and-tour-the-mandrake-project-3502111">&#39;The Mandrake Project&#39;</a> , and will mark Dickinson&#39;s first solo album in 18 years, following on from 2005&#39;s &#39;Tyranny Of Souls&#39;. </p><figure id="attachment_3536023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3536023" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3536023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="Bruce Dickinson performs with Iron Maiden" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Bruce-Dickinson@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3536023" class="wp-caption-text"> Bruce Dickinson performs with Iron Maiden. CREDIT: Francesco Castaldo\Archivio Francesco Castaldo\Mondadori via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Earlier this week, Dickinson has teased the forthcoming lead single <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-bruce-dickinson-announces-solo-single-afterglow-of-ragnarok-uk-ireland-tour-tickets-3532054">&#39;Afterglow Of Ragnarok&#39; and confirmed details of an upcoming tour</a> .</p><p> The live shows will kick off in spring 2024, with five shows across the UK – starting at the Barrowland Ballroom in Glasgow on May 18, and continuing the following day at the O2 Academy in Manchester.</p><p> From there, performances at Swansea Arena, Nottingham&#39;s Rock City and London&#39;s O2 Forum Kentish Town are all scheduled, before a run of shows across Europe. These include stops in France, Holland, Hungary, Sweden, Germany and more. Find a full list of shows and buy tickets <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbruce-dickinson-tickets%2Fartist%2F734920" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-bruce-dickinson-to-star-in-abba-horror-movie-bjorn-of-the-dead-3536021">Iron Maiden&#39;s Bruce Dickinson to star in ABBA-inspired horror movie &#39;Bjorn Of The Dead&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
